utstillingen, er det n\u00e5 lagt ut kondolanseprotokoll.", "Ole Sj\u00f8lie har dessverre g\u00e5tt bort, men hans kunstnerskap har satt evig spor. V\u00e5r dypeste medf\u00f8lelse g\u00e5r til Oles p\u00e5r\u00f8rende.", "Trondheim kunstmuseum", "Johan B\u00f6rjesson (direkt\u00f8r) og Cathrine Hovdahl Vik (konservator)"]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "folk"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "eeccee0b7b8627361c6524c81203d0cb1cca6aecc80f28d3ba6b61bf3b90dc94"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-05-02T07:05:09.000Z"}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/folk/article11807526.ece/hbyw9/ALTERNATES/w980-default/JPS-sj%C3%B8li2.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/1491003e9a7b7f6f610474d673feb538985b26a4.jpg?59082fa5"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Minneord: Ole Sj\u00f8lie -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "1491003e9a7b7f6f610474d673feb538985b26a4"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": "Minneord"}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "Minneord"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "folk"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "arts-and-entertainment"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["maleri", "utdannelse", "museet"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["statens kunstakademi", "europa og afrika", "kunstskolen", "gr\u00e5m\u00f8lna", "fagerborg"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["trondheim", "oslo", "norge", "fauske"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["ole sj\u00f8lie", "jean heiberg", "harald krohg stabell"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": "folk"}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/folk/article11807526.ece/hbyw9/ALTERNATES/w980-default/JPS-sj%C3%B8li2.jpg"}, {"field": "og-locale", "value": "nb_NO"}, {"field": "og-site-name", "value": "adressa.no"}, {"field": "og-title", "v